    write: IOPS=202k, BW=787MiB/s (826MB/s)(46.1GiB/60012msec); 0 zone resets
     bw (  KiB/s): min=498714, max=1199892, per=100.00%, avg=806659.03, stdev=4229.94, samples=3808
